\end_inset

 produces a 
\series bold
covariance
\series default
 
\series bold
matrix
\series default
 
\begin_inset Formula $K(\mathbf{x}_{*},\mathbf{x}_{*})$
\end_inset

 when evaluated at the vector 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{x}_{*}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

